bat

The bat to which these statistics apply. Applies a lazy loading protocol for recordings and sessions which only get populated from bat when they are first accesses. If they have been initialised to empty collections (or full collections) before the bat is entered then they will be updated to the correct data for the bat being entered. Similalry for the stats.
